as/ef61bea62463620cdcb89eed2facc8fb.poster.avif?t=1558465740\" width=616 height=410 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1065930/extras/ef61bea62463620cdcb89eed2facc8fb.webm?t=1558465740\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1065930/extras/ef61bea62463620cdcb89eed2facc8fb.mp4?t=1558465740\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >About key assignment</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>[Keyboard]<br>Move: Axis Key<br>attack1(sword): z<br>attack2(bullet): x<br>bomb: c<br>Open Console In Game: /<br>Slow Motion: left shift<br>self-destruction: p<br><br>submit: enter<br>pause: esc<br><br><br></li><li>[Xbox]<br>Move: Left Stick<br>attack1(sword): X<br>attack2(bullet): B<br>bomb: A<br>Open Console In Game: Y<br>Slow Motion: LB or RB<br>self-destruction: RS_B<br><br>submit: B<br>pause: start<br><br><br></li><li>[PS4]<br>Move: Left Stick<br>attack1(sword): ◯<br>attack2(bullet): ×<br>bomb: □<br>Open Console In Game: △<br>Slow Motion: L1 or R1<br>self-destruction: GamePad<br><br>submit: ×<br>pause: option</li></ul></li></ul>",
